A man is in critical condition following a collision between two trucks towards Bloemfontein on Tuesday.It is understood that one truck crashed into a stationary truck s trailer.On arrival paramedics found a man believed to be in his 20&#8217;s trapped in one of the trucks.ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring said fire and rescue used the jaws of life to extricate the man from the vehicle.The man sustained injuries on his head and a partial amputation on his left arm. He was provided with advanced life support treatment and transported to hospital for further medical care .Authorities on scene for further investigations.-TNA Reporter